@gretathunberg says she finds it 'strange' how we are supposed to look up to the UK on the matter of climate change.

Speaking exclusively to Sky News, the 18-year-old says the British government are 'climate villains', claiming the climate crisis 'more or less started in the UK' during the industrial revolution.

